    "Name": "Pouncer",
    "Details": "The G configuration of the Pouncer combines three Improved Heavy and three Pulse Medium Lasers with four SRM-4 launchers. Although an impressive damage potential, it can seldom be fired as a full Alpha Strike due to the limited cooling potential.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Aerial Assault</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.03</color></b>\n\n<br><br><color=#FFEF00>Arm Actuator Limits: Omni</color>\n\n",
